=== THINK BEFORE YOU SUMMARIZE ===

Before writing, perform this mental scan:

1. CLASSIFY — What type of legal document is this? (NDA, MSA, SOW, Employment Agreement, Lease, etc.)
2. IDENTIFY PARTIES — Who is involved and what are their roles?
3. EXTRACT OBLIGATIONS — What does each party commit to?
4. SCAN DATES — Effective date, expiration, renewal, notice periods?
5. SPOT RISKS — Unusual clauses, one-sided terms, missing protections?

